### 注册用户1
POST http://localhost:5637/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customId": "user1",
  "displayName": "用户1",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "user1@example.com"
}

### 注册用户2
POST http://localhost:5637/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customId": "user2", 
  "displayName": "用户2",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "user2@example.com"
}

### 用户1登录
POST http://localhost:5637/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customId": "user1",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {% client.global.set("user1_token", response.body.accessToken); %}

### 用户2登录
POST http://localhost:5637/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customId": "user2",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {% client.global.set("user2_token", response.body.accessToken); %}

### 用户1添加用户2为好友
POST http://localhost:5637/api/social/add-friend
Authorization: Bearer {{user1_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "user2",
  "isInformal": false
}

### 检查用户1的联系人列表
GET http://localhost:5637/api/social/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{user1_token}}

### 检查用户2的联系人列表
GET http://localhost:5637/api/social/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{user2_token}}

### 测试informal私聊（用户1添加用户2为informal好友）
POST http://localhost:5637/api/social/add-friend
Authorization: Bearer {{user1_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "user2",
  "isInformal": true
}

